#: knights_of_the_silver_spire\_main.cfg:32
msgid ""
"The story of the Knights of the Silver Spire and their battles against the "
"evil Crimson Duke to keep the Northlands safe.\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 9 scenarios, 3 endings)."
msgstr ""
"銀の尖塔騎士団が、Northland の安全を守るため、邪悪な Crimson Duke の一味と戦"
"闘を繰り広げる物語です．\n"
"\n"
"(中級、9シナリオ、3エンディング）"

